Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.48,0:24:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你啊 清
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.58,0:24:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们居然以这种样子相见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.92,0:24:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.84,0:24:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.91,0:24:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.36,0:24:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不再怨恨了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.72,0:24:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来 你怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.50,0:24:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.68,0:24:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.42,0:25:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 纸气球 轻轻飘
